File: Lieutenant-Colonel Charl Kinnear was assassinated outside his home last week. JOHANNESBURG - The Hawks say it can neither confirm nor deny that an arrest has been in connection with the death of Lieutenant-Colonel Charl Kinnear. READ: R1m reward for info leading to arrest of Kinnear killers The Daily Maverick is reporting that a suspect was arrested on Tuesday. The publication says he was apprehended in Johannesburg and will be transferred to Cape Town. Kinnear was assassinated outside his home last week. The Hawks say it will issue a statement on the matter soon. This is a developing story.